  "text": "Protein and RNA analyses. Protein extraction, quantification, and Western blot analysis were performed as previously described [CITATION_1] . Equal amounts of total protein (50 g) were loaded into each protein lane, and after electrophoresis, proteins were transferred onto a polyvinylidene difluoride membrane, and Western blot analysis was performed. An amido black-stained membrane or nonspecific cross-reacting bands were used as loading controls.",
